// controls.pickers.json — shared picker/selection control library text.
// Files: LemoineColorPickerPanel.xaml.cs, LemoineColorPickerWindow.xaml.cs, LemoineSwatchPicker.xaml.cs,
//        LemoineBrowserTreePicker.xaml.cs, LemoineMultiSelectTabs.xaml.cs, LemoineTagChipInput.xaml.cs.
//
// NOTE — deliberately left in code (not externalized):
//  - LemoineSwatchPicker's shape/fill kind tokens ("square","circle","tri","line","dash","solid","hatch","dots")
//    are persisted/logic tokens compared with == and fed straight into LemoineSwatchGlyph's Kind/Fill props;
//    the FILL row's own visible label reuses that same token as its text, so translating it would desync the
//    displayed word from the stored/compared value.
//  - LemoineColorPickerPanel's XML persistence tag/attribute names ("ColorSets","Set","Slot","RecentColors",
//    "Color","activeIndex","name") and every "#RRGGBB"-style hex format string are data, not prose.
//  - Segoe MDL2 / Unicode glyphs used icon-only (▾ ▸ × + ✕ ◐ ✓) stay in code per CLAUDE.md convention.
//  - LemoineLog.* context strings (e.g. "ColorPicker: load saved swatches") are diagnostics-only, out of scope.
